style=\"color: red;\">姓何嘅同班元朗八鄉指揮官當然係班黑社會嘅保護傘</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smCP4gA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsmCP4gA.png&h=749c2400&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xwh4S9V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwh4S9V.png&h=0ee3805a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，維尼用呢招嘅目的當然係同「老虎蒼蠅一起打」嘅肅貪活動目的動機差不多。但我地亦可以利用呢場運動嘅口號去肅清元朗，文宣組亦可以多加想像力去宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要以子之矛，攻子之盾！令肅清元朗變成一場保皇黨無法反對嘅一場正義之戰！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"大家都知中共慣常手段係用群眾鬥群眾，市民互鬥令大家轉移視線，令大家焦點變得模糊，再利用香港人金魚記憶特性，從而冷處理大家訴求。<br />\n<br />\n點樣將民怨由黑社會轉移到警方係重中之重<br />\n<br />\n試諗吓<br />\n黑社會無差別打人固然要圍剿<br />\n但警察隻眼開隻眼閉更加人神共憤<br />\n<br />\n燒村會有noise<br />\n但大家同班黑社會無差別攻擊嘅有咩分別<br />\n而且正中下懷<br />\n<br />\n之前有巴打講過清新元朗我覺得可以從呢方面入手"},{"pid":"5a06fb10a0e5f142231f0228fdae1b74a7a73441","tid":1354626,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"清新太軟弱 肅清好d"},{"pid":"a4abdb0532a2cb9b64975a278f686fcfb111d16b","tid":1354626,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74c9c7975c59095e565f914a5e849c887c6f7d1e","tid":1354626,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"77b7add0c1e26db41fdb901b107be1102502be40","tid":1354626,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:41:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f48e0dde959e32afc62a1a144e136c1ec35318d9","tid":1354626,"uid":93958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faeda2769b104cb5533adf42649635c2bfdddad","tid":1354626,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:48:57.000Z","msg